  m_Name: BlueNPC
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPCDialogue
  npcName: Blue Dude
  dialogueLines:
  - Hey! How are you doing?
  - That's great! Are you looking for kiwis?
  - Here, you can have mine!
  - Are you sure? You'll need it later.
  - Enjoy your day!
  - Oh no! What's wrong?
  - Oh! I have one, you can have it!
  - You know what can help? Kiwis!
  - 'I hope it made your day a bit better! '
  - Straight to the point, eh?
  - Fine, jeez, just take it.
  - I understand, take your Kiwi.
  - Just leave me alone.
